The fall production at Friends Academy this year is <em>The 25th Annual Putnam County Spelling Bee</em>. A hysterical play full of jokes and great music,<em> The 25th Annual Putnam County Spelling Bee</em> details the interactions of a few  stereotypical young spellers in their county spelling bee. This will be the first post in a series that will include first hand updates on how the rehearsals are going and other news about the show. Another one of Inkwell's very own, Nick McNiel, will be starring in it, as well as other Upper School students from all grades.

