Welcome to Inkwell 2.0!  This year we are launching with an entirely new website created by Editor in Chief Kyle Rosenbluth and a brand new editorial staff. Our primary goal for this year is to build up our readership. Thus, we plan to diverge from the run-of-the-mill articles that characterized past editions of our school newspaper.  Inkwell 2.0 will feature more multimedia content than ever before: videos, quizzes, comedy skits (courtesy of class clown Perry Gordon), movie and music reviews,  and social media updates (Facebook, Twitter, Instagram) provided by senior correspondent Bel Evans. This year we hope to develop a regular readership through providing the Friends community with a revamped Inkwell that will grab the your attention and keep you coming back week after week.

Thanks for reading!

